Keyboardist/vocalist Kerri Mack left the group in April 2007 after recording the album, and was replaced with keyboardist/vocalist Alida Marroni.
The group benefited heavily from online buzz and ferocious touring; it was named band of the day by SPIN on April 27, 2007, and has received many reviews from press sites.
